                <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-600 mb-8">
                    The Blue Ocean framework involves changing the value curve by eliminating, reducing, raising, and creating factors. This chart visualizes how the Black & White™ strategy diverges from the industry standard. Use the buttons to filter the strategy.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 mb-8">
