                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">The Canvas Profile</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">A dynamic, evolving work of art instead of a static grid. It's a visual biography of the user's creative journey.</p>
                    <button data-feature="canvas" class="show-example-btn text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 underline hover:text-gray-600">Show Example →</button>
                    <div class="example-section">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Example: User Journey</h4>
                        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 text-sm">
                            <li>A user posts a "Black" reel of a minimal cityscape. Their Canvas adds a sharp, geometric shape to its composition.</li>
                            <li>They follow a "White" music artist. Their Canvas gains a splash of bright color and a fluid line, reflecting the artist's sound.</li>
