                    <button data-feature="duality" class="show-example-btn text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 underline hover:text-gray-600">Show Example →</button>
                    <div class="example-section">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Example: Feed Interaction</h4>
                        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 text-sm">
                            <li>The user opens the app feeling relaxed. They land on the "Black" side of the feed, seeing calming architecture and ambient music clips.</li>
                            <li>With a quick swipe, they cross into the "White" feed. The content instantly shifts to vibrant fashion shows and upbeat, experimental art reels.</li>
                            <li>A creator posts an "In-Between" video of a dark forest with a single beam of light. This content appears on both feeds, acting as a bridge.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">The "In-Between" Moment</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">A new content format that connects two contrasting elements, embodying the core brand philosophy of duality.</p>
                    <button data-feature="inbetween" class="show-example-btn text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 underline hover:text-gray-600">Show Example →</button>
                    <div class="example-section">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Example: Creative Workflow</h4>
                        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 text-sm">
