                        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 text-sm">
                            <li>A digital artist collaborates with the brand on a one-of-a-kind virtual jacket. The jacket drops on the app like a sneaker release.</li>
                            <li>Users "buy" the digital version, which they can wear in their AR-enhanced reels and on their Canvas profile.</li>
                            <li>Exclusive collectors are given the option to purchase the physical, limited-edition jacket that corresponds to their digital ownership.</li>
